
1. Create a new connection to MQTT broker.
2. Create a new Dashboard.
3. Dashboard Configuration.
4. Add all necessary panels.

Example panel Relais 1:
Panel Name: Relais 1
Topic: Order
Payload on: rel1
Payload off: rel5
x Use icon switch
On Icon  green
Off icon  red
Icon size:  Medium
QoS:  0

Example panel Command / Resp:
Panel Name: Command / Resp
Topic: order / resp
x Show received timestamp
